languages.text: «Puede descansar aquí antes de regresar a Janus. Me aseguraré de que el Factótum atienda a todas sus necesidades».
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."

languages.text: 「ヤヌスに戻るまで、我が客人としてゆっくりと休んでほしい。ファクトタムがあらゆる要望に対応するよう取り計らおう」
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."

languages.text: “回加努斯之前，在这里好好休息休息，享受一下款待吧。无论你有什么突发奇想，我都会让高阶顾问满足你的要求。”
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."

languages.text: "Seid mein Gast und ruht Euch aus, ehe Ihr nach Janus zurückkehrt. Ich sorge dafür, dass Euch das Faktotum jeden Wunsch erfüllt."
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."

languages.text: « Je vous invite à vous reposer avant de retourner sur Janus. Je veillerai à ce que le factotum réponde à toutes vos demandes. »
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."

languages.text: "Rahatına bak ve Janus'a dönmeden önce güzelce dinlen. Kâhyanın tüm ihtiyaçlarınla ilgilenmesini sağlayacağım."
languages.original_text: "Be my guest and rest properly before your return to Janus. I will see that the Factotum attends to your every whim."
